{"tid":2517234,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"遇過最好/最仆街嘅老師係點？","createTime":"2021-05-05T07:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T09:17:19.000Z","uid":371485,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"21f2bb992bf9132992708d86820412ae388caf96","tid":2517234,"uid":371485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:57:33.000Z","msg":"有個英文老師無時無刻都好care學生，同佢吹水9up都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好掛住中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"5138aca5651eaa3b286d3827195acbc9a5c00a98","tid":2517234,"uid":306565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:00:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾矮仔日日9up 唔教書<br />\n自己矮自尊感極低淨係笑鳩學生<br />\n得閒就抽你水/講你壞話<br />\n高中三年中文都唔知學咗啲乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd6cf3cfa3fd136958317acdada4979de53d903","tid":2517234,"uid":219842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:11:16.000Z","msg":"同我講打份工冇用 最緊要識人。識投資"},{"pid":"600dd6b291a98a95a08e13d027a0952937881c1e","tid":2517234,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:16:10.000Z","msg":"中二定三, 全年英文只寫copy book同叫人企起身讀課文, 其他野叫人自修"},{"pid":"53cd466ed31621250cd4fd817354b41cdb2d085c","tid":2517234,"uid":62318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbd6cf3cfa3fd136958317acdada4979de53d903","tid":2517234,"uid":219842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:11:16.000Z","msg":"同我講打份工冇用 最緊要識人。識投資"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:16:33.000Z","msg":"依個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1489eb07427527cc76fd4688cb932cc582427d","tid":2517234,"uid":369444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"基本上冇乜點教書 <br />\n有時上個半鐘嘅堂教一個鐘就話自修<br />\n考DSE前全班作左兩篇文俾佢改<br />\n之後都一直未收到 全班日鳩日催佢先肯考之前三日叫我哋返學校攞"},{"pid":"09e5c98ab768c34f1a48171cb32fb1e002592640","tid":2517234,"uid":381069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:32:24.000Z","msg":"佢係俗稱老屎忽<br />\n<br />\n老屎忽有嘅點佢都有<br />\n<br />\n基本上冇乜點教書<br />\n<br />\n因為唔係主科<br />\n<br />\n一個學期得一份功課<br />\n<br />\n佢仲要hea改<br />\n<br />\n佢對其他人好西<br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解對我好好<br />\n<br />\n仲成日請我食野<br />\n<br />\n仲要唔平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同我講唔少做人處事道理<br />\n<br />\n唔識點報答你"},{"pid":"40bcf1e95a54000ca00286e0837f8265278d5886","tid":2517234,"uid":193310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:35:29.000Z","msg":"中學有個老師平時好惡<br />\n好唔鐘意上佢堂<br />\n<br />\n後尾屋企出左D事<br />\n佢係最關心我個個<br />\n仲寫卡仔俾我叫我要堅強"},{"pid":"a08d144f6aed016e9db885e132d92017b5600d02","tid":2517234,"uid":107469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:42:31.000Z","msg":"中學有個教英文miss 自己好似感冒定唔知點 失晒聲<br />\n撞正個日要TSA(唔記得係咪, 總之有個試要考)<br />\n正路既老師都係會call sick然後補考<br />\n但係佢去左打開聲針死頂返黎, 然後個下覺得佢真係好有heart<br />\n<br />\n最撚仆街既老師係有次早會早左完 第一堂係lab黎 但係個陣未夠鐘上第一堂 所以我係班房坐到夠鐘先上去lab<br />\n上到去 點知全班都已經係上面上緊堂 我係最後一個先上到去<br />\n然後條仆街就屌鳩我話成班都到左你做乜鳩遲到 但係其實我係準時 只係其他撚樣早到"},{"pid":"3f2926f947fde3d02da5a86111c71318815901e5","tid":2517234,"uid":386893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21f2bb992bf9132992708d86820412ae388caf96","tid":2517234,"uid":371485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:57:33.000Z","msg":"有個英文老師無時無刻都好care學生，同佢吹水9up都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好掛住中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:47:47.000Z","msg":"咁好既老師都有？<br />\n樓主而家讀緊咩先？<br />\n中學以外老師同同學關係真係無咁close"},{"pid":"89190e349a7755619bc84baca7ab7b11a9b9e6d9","tid":2517234